<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="7Aug1940"><font color="red">7 August 1940</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to James Johnson Sweeney): I sent two airmail letters yesterday to N.Y., one to Mr Cerf, one to the Viking Press &hellip; I also asked Mr Cerf for an advance of royalties &hellip; I have asked the Swiss authorities whether they permit British subjects to enter Switzerland &hellip; no reply has come after about 20 days </div>
